Memorable Mother’s Day in Portugal with @arichey and the twins ✨🇵🇹 After 7 days at sea we made it to the island São Miguel in the Azores. The streets were lined with flowers and everyone was out enjoying this amazing azorean day. Seemed only fitting that we landed here on Mother’s Day - a perfect way to appreciate having @arichey in our lives and for blessing us with her beauty and kindness. The twins love you mama and I’m forever grateful that you’re their mother. nós te amamos @arichey 🤍

in a blink of an eye they are 2🥹 I can’t even handle it, I can’t believe it! feels like yesterday I was holding my little 4 lb twinners🥹🥹🥹 and now they are 2 year olds! I always wondered what it would be like have two year olds! I would see other twin moms with two year olds and it would seem so far away, so impossible! and now here I am.. with two sweet, curious, fiery, strong, cuddly, little chatter boxes that follow me around all day😍 I love seeing their relationship grow, Zara walks around saying Zane’s bouy and doesn’t let zane get too far away without saying “zane come back!” ahaha and their very big on which toys are Zara’s and which ones are Zane’s and they’ll go hand the toy to the other if its not theirs hahah they’re so much fun! love books, coloring and being outside, they love aunts, uncles, cousins and grandmas! Obsessed with Disney and repeat everything we say! Turing more and more into my little besties everyday! I love every single version of them I’ve known so far.. and can’t wait to meet every version of them I haven’t met yet!🥹 who has been here since they were born?!

happy SECOND star to the right birthday twinners!!✨💫 we had the cutest best party surrounded by so many people who love these two🥹 we have a very happy Peter + Tink! and they both are refusing to take the costumes off haha I love watching them be little, I love their smiles, I love their little voices and how they mispronounce words!! I love the way they say mommy and I love how much they love each other! never grow up my little two year olds!

!!!! I am excited about my @tempo move home gym to help me get moving everyday! I haven’t worked out since before I got pregnant with the twins!🙈and as a momma of two toddlers and business owner.. finding time to workout can sometimes be impossible! I love that the twins like to do this with me and copy me as I do the workouts! I love how beautiful it is and looks great in my living room!! There are so many fun classes on the app! The app tracks your heart rate, movement, and weights through your camera! It’s very customizable and easy to use! & we got you a code!! use FACK35 for 35% off any hardware bundle at tempo.fit !!

I love watching them do life together!! Nothing more rewarding than watching them grow up at the same time!!! when I was looking through all these videos of them growing up I started choosing all my favorite little everyday moments of them. And they all ended up being Zane and Zara side by side doing something together.. crawling, walking, laughing, eating, playing, laying on me and i just thought of how much of a blessing it is that they have each other and how grateful I am that God trusted me to be the one to get to watch them grow!

a happy little life we have with these two🥹 someone said to take the videos you’ve taken recently and use this template to see what a beautiful life you have!! so you should do it too!! I believe that happiness comes with finding the happy tiny moments in everyday

Remembering the good old days while we’re still in them 🙌🏻 My favorite part of bike rides is when we pass through tunnels and we all make monkey noises in the echo. Zane loves sitting in the front and Zara gets a kick out of poking Zane in the back of the head through the holes in his seat. They won’t go until their feet are buckled in tight tight tight and always love going fast like dash!!
